2D Piping Designers
2D Piping Designers
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Salary:  Mobilisation/ Demobilisation flightsAir Energi are recruiting for 2D Piping Designers to be based in Abu Dhabi for a short term contract of 3-4 months.
The position is to start ASAP; candidates must be available to start the role within 2 weeks.
The successful candidate will have strong FEED and detailed design experience as well as previous onshore project experience.
The all inclusive rate for this role will be 150 - 200 USD per day dependant on experience. This is an all inclusive rate; mobilisation /de-mobilisation flights and visa will be provided but accommodation, local transport and general living costs in Abu Dhabi will be your responsibility.
The working week will be 5 days per week working 48 hours; you will only be paid for days that you work.
This position would suit someone that is immediately available.
